{"tid":160771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿示威者阻離開　工聯會麥美娟報警","createTime":"2017-03-18T04:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T07:37:47.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a630092ee05a38a6cfb295ac3ea5350cf9e548df","tid":160771,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T04:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170318/large/1489809905_26e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170318%2Flarge%2F1489809905_26e3.jpg&h=fc1ebe70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n財委會周五起審議涉及9,000多項工程的基本工程儲備基金撥款，當中包括備受爭議的元朗橫洲發展項目，會議晚上結束後一批橫洲村民向建制派議員示威，一度與警員推撞。工聯會麥美娟早上在4名黨友陪同下見傳媒，稱昨日離開時遇上阻撓，令她感到人身受威脅，事後已到中區警署報警，「尋日嘅情況係非常混亂同危險，有一班請願人士衝咗出嚟馬路，有人拍我車、敲我車窗，擾釀咗成10分鐘。」<br />\n<br />\n與麥美娟同車離開的陸頌雄就稱，「（示威者）成個人瞓咗車頭冚，完全有個客觀嘅行為係想阻止我同麥美娟離開立法會」，他強調議員受權力及特權法保障，前往及離開立法會都不能受阻。麥美娟批評示威者的行徑「非常危險，對議員人身安全受威脅」，故選擇報警要求警方正視有關安全問題，「我哋明白財委會尋日討論嘅事項，係會令到有市民有唔同嘅感受，但係當大家表達意見，希望大家以和平、理性、安全，最緊要係合法嘅方法去處理」。<br />\n<br />\n她又指經過佔中，法庭昨日亦就旺角騷亂作出判刑，相信市民都不想見到社會「有咁唔安全嘅地方」，故她選擇去報警，「大家可以有不同意見，但絕對不能夠用暴力或者非法嘅手段去脅迫他人、阻止他人去表達佢嘅意見。」"},{"pid":"9b53cbaa0a32932789357f18ec297769274203b8","tid":160771,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T04:36:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56445181&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170318\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56445181%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170318&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=a39e6d52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56445181%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170318&h=8b82e9a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56445181&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170318</a>"},{"pid":"ee51643c109a4cad642460cf68c64cb5d8bc613c","tid":160771,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T04:42:14.000Z","msg":"黑箱作業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c05075395fd932530184e6b43d1ed1dfde8182b","tid":160771,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T04:42:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad15e24b73f45751414617030a4351e27b7aae8f","tid":160771,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T04:43:33.000Z","msg":"又騙錢"},{"pid":"a54c0491f8e720791a5935179ddf4902052ef6bc","tid":160771,"uid":92377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T05:07:00.000Z","msg":"屌呢個死臭化閪"},{"pid":"092b477bf6eed9e29c84d0f4139cf209d7670fa8","tid":160771,"uid":76181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T05:13:32.000Z","msg":"和平理性安全嘅表達方式你都唔撚聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d68fb4f075841bf5bc4813baaf1cc93cc6b79da","tid":160771,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T05:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cae6af3c6cf01f06e8e579d4226f1b6b78f9348","tid":160771,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T05:27:39.000Z","msg":"玻璃心, 家下係市民訓練佢EQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360683a44fb1327c5bfe5ca690aa92e7b3b7ab0f","tid":160771,"uid":7534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:31:38.000Z","msg":"老處女係戇撚鳩㗎啦，大家唔係唔知呀？"},{"pid":"e20ad57e893fdbb0096317c8f2a7adc8400ed6ad","tid":160771,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:37:47.000Z","msg":"咩事"}]}